answers.answer: It can be from your baby's head, that's what I have, but for me it hurts only in certain positions or when she feels like kicking me right in that spot. You should know, that other than that - pain under right rib, if you also have headache and higher blood pressure can be signs of preeclampsia. Go get checked just to be sure. Good luck. ;)
